'''Mduduzi Mabaso''' (yavutse 1 Mata 1976), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] . <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/mduduzi-mabaso</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime na teleserial ''Blood Diamond'', ''Machine Gun Preacher'' na ''[[Hotel Rwanda]]'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/catching-up-with-rhythm-citys-no1-tsotsi-suffo-20200909</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1976 i Alexandra, muri Afurika y'Epfo . Yamaze imyaka 3 y'ubwana bwe muri Transkei . <ref name="briefly">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://briefly.co.za/36408-mduduzi-mabaso-biography-age-son-wife-wife-rhythm-city-movies-nominations-awards-net-worth.html "Mduduzi Mabaso biography"]. briefly<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Yabanje gushyingiranwa na Veronica Maseko kandi bombi bafite abana babiri. Nyuma yashakanye na mugenzi we bakina filime, Fatima Metsileng. <ref>https://www.magzter.com/article/Entertainment/Drum-English/Love-Lives-Here</ref> Mabaso yamusanze mugihe cya shampiyona ya kabiri ya ''Zone 14'' muri 2007. <ref>https://zalebs.com/relationships/mduduzi-mabaso/rhythm-citys-mduduzi-mabaso-shares-how-his-wife-made-him-believe-love-again</ref> Bashyingiwe nyuma yimyaka mike babyara abana babiri. Rero, afite abana bane: Ntokozo, Mpumi, Njabulo na Zolile. <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/36408-mduduzi-mabaso-biography-age-son-wife-wife-rhythm-city-movies-nominations-awards-net-worth.html </ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1992, yagaragaye bwa mbere mu ikinamico ''Divide na Rule'' . Mu 2004, yatangiye gukina filime muri firime y'Abanyamerika ''Hotel Rwanda'' iyobowe na Terry George . Iyi filime yari ishingiye kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yo]] mu [[Rwanda]], yabaye muri mata 1994. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20080430050749/http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=7112</ref> Hanyuma yakinnye mubikorwa byinshi byunganira muri firime, ''Catch a Fire'', ''Heartlines'' and ''Blood Diamond'' . <ref name="briefly">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://briefly.co.za/36408-mduduzi-mabaso-biography-age-son-wife-wife-rhythm-city-movies-nominations-awards-net-worth.html "Mduduzi Mabaso biography"]. briefly<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Yakinnye kandi mumikino yo kuri stage: ''Cry The Beloved Country'', ''Madiba’s Magic'', ''Behind the Curtains'', ''Shaka Zulu'' and ''Tasha On The Rocks'' . <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=6613</ref>

Muri 2006, yagize uruhare runini muri make ''Sekalli le Meokgo'' iyobowe na Tebho Mahlatsi. <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/236788643</ref> Iyi filime yaje guhabwa Filime ngufi nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Durban 2007. <ref>http://www.artlink.co.za/news_article.htm?contentID=3883</ref>

Mu 2007, yatumiriwe gukina mu isonga kuri televiziyo yo muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]]  ''Rhythm City'' . Yakinnye nka 'Suffocate Ndlovu'. yakoze premier yayo kuri tereviziyo yubusa kuri televiziyo e.tv ku ya 9 Nyakanga 2007. Uruhererekane rugenda rwerekanwa muri Afrika yepfo hamwe nibisobanuro byiza. Hagati aho, Mabaso yatsindiye igihembo cya Golden Horn igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu isabune ya TV hanyuma igihembo cya Golden Horn kikaba umukinnyi mwiza muri Filime yerekana uruhare rwe 'Ndlovu' muri serial.

